.com/photo/msid-130870482,imgsize-168456.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Clavicular charged in shocking Everglades shooting stream, faces up to 1 year in jail]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130870046.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kick streamer Braden Eric Peters, also known as Clavicular, is in legal trouble. He is charged with unlawfully firing a gun in a public place. The incident occurred in the Florida Everglades during a livestream. Wildlife officials investigated the viral video. Peters' lawyers state he followed a guide's instructions and no harm occurred. The case highlights livestream consequences.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/clavicular-charged-in-shocking-everglades-shooting-stream-faces-up-to-1-year-in-jail/articleshow/130870046.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/clavicular-charged-in-shocking-everglades-shooting-stream-faces-up-to-1-year-in-jail/articleshow/130870046.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T02:06:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130870031,imgsize-464510.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Comparing H-1B workers...': Row over claim visa holders are less than 0.5% of US jobs]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130869861.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/comparing-h-1b-workers-to-entire-workforce-row-over-us-entrepreneurs-claim-visa-holders-are-less-than-0-5-of-jobs/articleshow/130869861.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/comparing-h-1b-workers-to-entire-workforce-row-over-us-entrepreneurs-claim-visa-holders-are-less-than-0-5-of-jobs/articleshow/130869861.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T01:58:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130869902,imgsize-189752.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ted Turner and legacy of WCW: How he revolutionized wrestling, created nWo, and challenged Vince McMahon]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130865695.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ted Turner, the media mogul behind CNN, TNT, and TBS, has died at 87. He transformed professional wrestling by turning WCW into a national rival to WWF, launching Monday Nitro and the nWo era. Turner’s hands-off approach, cultural insight, and media empire permanently reshaped wrestling and television. He is survived by five children, 14 grandchildren, and two great-grandchildren.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/ted-turner-and-the-legacy-of-wcw-how-he-revolutionized-wrestling-created-nwo-and-challenged-vince-mcmahon/articleshow/130865695.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/ted-turner-and-the-legacy-of-wcw-how-he-revolutionized-wrestling-created-nwo-and-challenged-vince-mcmahon/articleshow/130865695.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-07T01:51:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130869632,imgsize-657564.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[JasonTheWeen, Marlon, StableRonaldo under fire for running red light and stop sign on stream]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130869450.cms" /&gt;